I am passionate about the environment. I try to divert as much as possible from the landfill, and use what you already have in your home to store your stuff.
Is clutter taking over your life? Get in touch with me today!

profile:
I am here to help. It's that simple.

My main focus is to help you simplify your life and support you in achieving your goals. As your lifestyle consultant or coach, I tailor my services to your particular needs.

Personalized services range from decluttering, downsizing and organizing to time management, work & life balance as well as health & wellness support.

My lifestyle management company offers both virtual lifestyle coaching and professional organizing consultations as well as in-person services to a growing local clientele in Peterborough, Ontario and the surrounding area (Lakefield, Ennismore, Buckhorn, Bobcaygeon, Lindsay, Fenelon Falls, Orono, Bowmanville, Newcastle, Courtice, Clarington, Cobourg, Port Hope, Roseneath, Norwood, Havelock, Hastings, Campbellford, Warkworth etc.)

My lifestyle services support and aim to inspire mindfulness, simplicity and the pursuit of a more sustainable, balanced lifestyle.

Consider me, whether you need some professional coaching, consulting or are simply looking to achieve a more balanced lifestyle with some physical help. 

My company prides itself on customer satisfaction, repeat business and referrals.
